OL,3,CNew care hubs tackle shortage of GP
OL,4,Cappointments and hospital pressures
OL,6,FHospitals at Treliske and Derriford
OL,7,Fhave both declared critical incidents
OL,8,Fin recent weeks, so to reduce the
OL,9,Fpressure, the NHS in Cornwall has set
OL,10,Fup a number of primary care hubs, for
OL,11,Fpeople who need to be seen on the day,
OL,12,Fbut can't get a doctor's appointment.
OL,14,FBob Burgess from Saltash tripped on a
OL,15,Frock and broke his ankle while taking
OL,16,Fphotographs.
