OL,3,CNew care hubs tackle shortage of GP
OL,4,Cappointments and hospital pressures
OL,6,FA neighbour took him to the primary
OL,7,Fcare hub at Bodmin Hospital, where he
OL,8,Fwas seen and had his foot put in
OL,9,Fplaster in less than two and a half
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,12,FBob has also had a hospital bed
OL,13,Fdelivered to his home because it's not
OL,14,Fsafe for him to go upstairs.
OL,16,FBob said: "At the end of the day, my
OL,17,Fcondition wasn't that serious enough
OL,18,Fto warrant a stay in hospital and I'd
OL,19,Frather be in that home in my own
OL,20,Fenvironment, surrounded by my friends
OL,21,Fand everything."
