OL,3,CNew care hubs tackle shortage of GP
OL,4,Cappointments and hospital pressures
OL,6,FHe was full of praise for the new
OL,7,Funit, adding: "From the time I got
OL,8,Finto Bodmin to the time I left Bodmin,
OL,9,FI was absolutely looked after, no
OL,10,Fissues at all, cared for, given the
OL,11,Finjections, given tablets and
OL,12,Feverything."
OL,14,FThe Primary Care Hub at Bodmin has
OL,15,Falready treated more than 200 patients
OL,16,Fsince it opened in December.
OL,18,FThis includes Lisa Davey, who was
OL,19,Freferred to the hub by her doctor's
OL,20,Fsurgery with a suspected chest
OL,21,Finfection.
