OL,3,CNew care hubs tackle shortage of GP
OL,4,Cappointments and hospital pressures
OL,6,FLisa could not see her normal GP
OL,7,Fbecause they did not have any on the
OL,8,Fday appointments available.
OL,10,FShe said: "It doesn't bother me. I
OL,11,Fdon't think I've seen the same person
OL,12,Ffor a long time, but that's absolutely
OL,13,Ffine as long as I'm getting seen and
OL,14,Ftreated."
OL,16,FHubs have also been set up in St
OL,17,FAustell, Helston, and Redruth, with
OL,18,Fmore planned.
