OL,3,CNew care hubs tackle shortage of GP
OL,4,Cappointments and hospital pressures
OL,6,FThis is just one of the ways the NHS
OL,7,Fis trying to deal with the traditional
OL,8,Fwinter pressures and reduce the number
OL,9,Fof people going to hospital.
OL,11,FDr Janine Glazier said: "It is linking
OL,12,Fup all the different organisations
OL,13,Fthat are in Cornwall and seeing how we
OL,14,Fcan best work together.
