OL,3,CNew care hubs tackle shortage of GP
OL,4,Cappointments and hospital pressures
OL,6,F"Because in Cornwall, we don't have
OL,7,Fthe luxury of having lots of different
OL,8,Fcounties around us that we can borrow
OL,9,FGP's and nurse practitioners from. So,
OL,10,Fwe really have to work together to see
OL,11,Fif we can get as much capacity out of
OL,12,Four workforce as possible to treat our
OL,13,Fpatients."
OL,15,FDr Glazier added: "What we can do is
OL,16,Fmake sure that we see those patients
OL,17,Fwho might be admitted to hospital
OL,18,Flater on, and because we can see them
OL,19,Fvery quickly, we reduce the impact on
OL,20,Fthe hospital and reduce their chances
OL,21,Fof needing an admission."
